January 2007 Cyber Girl of the Month


Kortnie travels for fun as much as she can but she never lets herself stray too long from Orange County&#039;s beaches. "I live at the ocean," she says. "I scuba dive, go wakeboarding or just sit on the sand under the sun. Lately I&#039;ve been waking up early to work out, walk my dogs and drink a smoothie with a shot of wheatgrass. I love to make dinner after work and play golf on weekends and I try and fit as many things into my time as possible because, like my friends say, I live every day to the fullest!".
